Datametrics Corp said it wona 4.9-mln-dlr contract from the U.S. Army.    The company said Datametrics will deliver printer/plottersto the Army's Redstone Arsenal, beginning in September, 1987.    Datametrics said it had a record backlog of funded andunfunded projects of 31.8 mln dlrs on March 1, 1987. Reuter&#3;